      <h1 class='title'>Armed Forces Pay Review Body</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 14 March 2003 vol 401 c29WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_29ws' title='Col. 29WS &mdash; HC Deb 14 March 2003 vol 401 c29WS' name='column_29ws' href='#column_29ws' rel='bookmark'>29WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0401P0-04993'>
        <a name='S6CV0401P0_20030314_CWS_1'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/dr-lewis-moonie' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0401P0_20030314_CWS_1' title='Link to this speech by Dr Lewis Moonie' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/dr-lewis-moonie" title="Dr Lewis Moonie">The Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State for Defence (Dr. Lewis Moonie)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0401P0-04993">I am pleased to announce that I have reappointed Lord Patel as a member of the Armed Forces Pay Review Body for a second three-year term. This appointment has been conducted in accordance with the Office of the Commissioner for Public Appointments' guidance on appointments to public bodies.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
